We need answers tonight, now.

554
00:43:22,544 --> 00:43:24,504
- Well, think of something.
- Glenn: Come on, let's go.

555
00:43:24,671 --> 00:43:27,757
- T-Dog: Let's get out of here.
- Glenn: Let's go. Please.

556
00:43:27,924 --> 00:43:30,385
- ( whirrs )
- Shane: All right, back to the cars.

557
00:43:30,552 --> 00:43:32,761
- Let's go. Move.
- The camera-- it moved.

558
00:43:32,928 --> 00:43:36,432
- You imagined it.
- It moved.

559
00:43:36,598 --> 00:43:39,226
- It moved.
- Rick, it is dead, man.

560
00:43:39,393 --> 00:43:42,521
It's an automated device.
It's gears, okay?

561
00:43:42,688 --> 00:43:44,188
They're just winding down.
Now come on.

562
00:43:44,355 --> 00:43:46,691
- No, just go away.
- Shane: Man, just listen to me.

563
00:43:46,858 --> 00:43:48,776
Look around this place.
It's dead, okay?

564
00:43:48,943 --> 00:43:51,362
It's dead.
You need to let it go, Rick.

565
00:43:51,529 --> 00:43:53,197
Lori:
Rick, there's nobody here!

566
00:43:53,364 --> 00:43:56,242
I know you're in there.
I know you can hear me.

567
00:43:56,409 --> 00:43:59,202
- Shane: Get back to the cars now!
- Rick: Please, we're desperate.

568
00:43:59,369 --> 00:44:01,538
Please help us.
We have women, children,

569
00:44:01,705 --> 00:44:03,707
- no food, hardly any gas left.
- Rick.

570
00:44:03,874 --> 00:44:05,374
- There's nobody here.
- We have nowhere else to go.

571
00:44:05,541 --> 00:44:07,543
- ( pounds on door )
- Shane: Keep your eyes open.

572
00:44:07,710 --> 00:44:10,379
If you don't let us in,
you're killing us!

573
00:44:10,546 --> 00:44:13,339
- Please!
- Shane: Come on, buddy, let's go.

574
00:44:13,506 --> 00:44:14,882
- Let's go.
- Rick: Please help us.

575
00:44:15,049 --> 00:44:16,884
( people shouting )

576
00:44:17,051 --> 00:44:20,137
You're killing us! You're killing us!

577
00:44:20,304 --> 00:44:22,431
You're killing us!

578
